and enjoy the program!

00:01:01.082 --> 00:01:04.919 line:90% position:50% align:center
Well, it’s an absolute delight
to be here today, isn’t it?

00:01:16.347 --> 00:01:19.559 line:90% position:50% align:center
And you’re going to get happier
as the morning goes along.

00:01:21.936 --> 00:01:24.147 line:90% position:50% align:center
The annual meeting

00:01:24.147 --> 00:01:28.526 line:90% position:50% align:center
—as an example,
I’m going to pick the year of 2013.

00:01:28.526 --> 00:01:33.281 line:90% position:50% align:center
Now, that annual meeting
has been called landmark.

00:01:34.032 --> 00:01:38.203 line:90% position:50% align:center
We’ve even stated that;
we called it a landmark annual meeting.

00:01:38.203 --> 00:01:40.580 line:90% position:50% align:center
You might think
that all annual meetings are landmark,

00:01:40.580 --> 00:01:42.582 line:90% position:50% align:center
