01:24:24.139 --> 01:24:27.851 line:90% position:50% align:center
We want elders
and ministerial servants and pioneers

01:24:27.851 --> 01:24:30.020 line:90% position:50% align:center
to take the lead in the ministry.

01:24:30.020 --> 01:24:32.105 line:90% position:50% align:center
But all of us

01:24:32.105 --> 01:24:37.110 line:90% position:50% align:center
in our personal ministry
want to be even more zealous

01:24:37.110 --> 01:24:41.656 line:90% position:50% align:center
in what we want
