01:24:42.365 --> 01:24:46.536 line:90% position:50% align:center
What an exciting time this is!

01:24:46.536 --> 01:24:49.080 line:90% position:50% align:center
The Governing Body sincerely hopes

01:24:49.080 --> 01:24:51.917 line:90% position:50% align:center
that many more will come to join us

01:24:51.917 --> 01:24:55.379 line:90% position:50% align:center
in serving Jehovah before the end comes.

01:24:55.379 --> 01:24:57.214 line:90% position:50% align:center
And remember:

01:24:57.214 --> 01:25:00.509 line:90% position:50% align:center
Jehovah delights in rewarding his people

01:25:00.509 --> 01:25:04.596 line:90% position:50% align:center
